{"lemma":"سُعُرُ","slug":"سُعُرُ","root":"س.ع.ر","root_slug":"س-ع-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ع-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سَعِير","root":"سعر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":16},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["name","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n19801","n19802","n19803","n19804","n19805"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8F%D8%B9%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"blaze"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fire"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"flame"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hell","examples":[{"text":"وَكَذَٰلِكَ أَوۡحَيۡنَآ إِلَيۡكَ قُرۡءَانًا عَرَبِيّٗا لِّتُنذِرَ أُمَّ ٱلۡقُرَىٰ وَمَنۡ حَوۡلَهَا وَتُنذِرَ يَوۡمَ ٱلۡجَمۡعِ لَا رَيۡبَ فِيهِۚ فَرِيقٞ فِي ٱلۡجَنَّةِ وَفَرِيقٞ فِي ٱلسَّعِيرِ.","english":"And thus We have inspired in thee a Lecture in Arabic, that thou mayst warn the mother-town and those around it, and mayst warn of a day of assembling whereof there is no doubt. A host will be in the Garden, and a host of them in the Flame."}]},{"pos":"name","gloss":"Seir"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Belongs to the root س ع ر (s ʕ r). Compare Hebrew סער (sá'ar, “storm, tempest”).\n\nFrom Hebrew שעיר."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19801","headword_ar":"سُعْرٌ","root":"sEr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suEaArN","text_ar":"سُعَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Madness, insanity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"demoniacal possession;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suEurN","text_ar":"سُعُرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) so ↓ the latter is expl. by AAF as used in the Kur liv. 47: and so it is expl. as used in verse 24 of the same chap.: (TA:) or it signifies in the former, (S,) or in the latter, (TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weariness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distress,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affliction, and punishment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, S, TA:) or, accord. to Az,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~aA A_i*aA lafiY DalaAlK wasuEurK","text_ar":"اـِنَّا اـِذَا لَفِى ضَلَالٍ وَسُعُرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in verse 24, may mean (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"verily we should in that case be in error, and in punishment"},{"kind":"text","text":"arising from what would necessarily befall us: or, accord. to Ibn-'Arafeh, it means,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state that would inflame and excite us."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hunger;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suEaArN","text_ar":"سُعَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Fr, K, TA:) or the former signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence of desire for flesh-meat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and ↓ the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence of hunger:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burning of hunger:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burning of thirst."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b4-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A disease, such as the mange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scab, that is transitive from one to another;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transition of the mange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scab,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other disease, from one to another;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EadowaY","text_ar":"عَدْوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K. [See 1.])"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","Fr"]},{"entry_id":"n19802","headword_ar":"سِعْرٌ","root":"sEr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"current price,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rate, at which a thing is to be sold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoEaArN","text_ar":"اَسْعَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, A, Msb, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu siEorN","text_ar":"لَهُ سِعْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is exceedingly valuable:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa lahu siEorN","text_ar":"لَيْسَ لَهُ سِعْرٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is exceedingly cheap."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["MA","K"]},{"entry_id":"n19803","headword_ar":"سَعَرٌ","root":"sEr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suEorapN","text_ar":"سُعْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n19804","headword_ar":"سَعِرٌ","root":"sEr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mad, insane,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possessed by a demon:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoEuwrapN","text_ar":"مَسْعُورَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a she-camel: (S:) or the latter, so applied,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that will not remain still;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suEurN","text_ar":"سُعُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning “ madness, or insanity, or demoniacal possession: ” (Ham p. 785:) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoEarN","text_ar":"مِسْعَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEirN","text_ar":"سَعِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEoraY","text_ar":"سَعْرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S"]},{"entry_id":"n19805","headword_ar":"سُعُرٌ","root":"sEr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suEorN","text_ar":"سُعْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}